# Deep imported JSON fixture

```scalascript
def wrapJson(level: Int, inner: String): String =
  if level <= 0 then inner
  else wrapJson(level - 1, "{\"next\":" + inner + "}")

val deepJsonDocument = wrapJson(18, "{\"value\":\"done\"}")
```
